147
00:05:59,620 --> 00:06:03,670
[Jialin]

148
00:06:08,150 --> 00:06:09,530
[Jialin]

149
00:06:12,830 --> 00:06:14,150
It's been a day.

150
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:16,200
