161
00:07:16,090 --> 00:07:16,830
Jialin.

162
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,250
You scared me.

163
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,130
Next time when you wait for someone secretly,

164
00:07:22,130 --> 00:07:24,260
