172
00:07:38,390 --> 00:07:39,350
Forget it.

173
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,180
Then, why are you here?

174
00:07:42,470 --> 00:07:43,600
Ye Han,

175
00:07:43,990 --> 00:07:46,300
