176
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:50,780
[Security, Surveillance Center]

177
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,680
I just want to have a look at him.

178
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,909
I was wondering

179
00:07:51,300 --> 00:07:53,220
