205
00:08:49,850 --> 00:08:50,720
I

206
00:08:50,750 --> 00:08:51,920
just want to know

207
00:08:51,940 --> 00:08:53,510
if you have had meals on time,

208
00:08:53,510 --> 00:08:54,740
